What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Ultralight and Light Aircraft Market?



Market Analysis and Insights :

Global Ultralight and Light Aircraft Market

Ultralight and light aircraft market will reach at an estimated value of USD 9,535.32 million by 2028 and grow at a CAGR of 7.20% in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Rise in the technological advancements and expansion of sales & services network acts as an essential factor driving the ultralight and light aircraft market.

Ultralight aviation is defined as the flying of lightweight, 1- or 2-seat fixed-wing aircraft. Rise in the concerns for pilot and passenger safety on account of several accidents of these aircrafts is the vital factor escalating the market growth.

Rise in the adoption of urban air mobility is a crucial factor accelerating the market growth, also rise in the tourism and sport flights, increase in the private jet industry and rise in the number of high net worth individuals (HNWI) are the major factors among others boosting the ultralight and light aircraft market. Moreover, rise in the advantages of hybrid-electric propulsion over traditional propulsion and increase in the technological developments in the field of drone payloads and passenger drones will further create new opportunities for ultralight and light aircraft market in the forecast period mentioned above.

However, fluctuations in the pattern of aircraft deliveries is the major factor among others restraining the market growth, and will further challenge the ultralight and light aircraft market in the forecast period mentioned above.

